name: Imprnt
description: Imprnt builds research-grade infrastructure for collaborative intelligence, enabling researchers, clinicians, AI agents, and traders to operate on verified evidence rather than trust. Our current products include: Verification engines (https://thescience.app/) Research publications discovery (https://discover.preprints.io/) Gamified AI benchmarking (https://SPHNX.ai/) Medical collaboration through our close partnership with SpineDAO
